Package model.medrecord

Class MedicalRecordEntry

java.lang.Object
model.BaseModel
model.medrecord.MedicalRecordEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Copyable, SerializableCopyable
public class MedicalRecordEntry extends BaseModel
Represents a medical record entry. A medical record entry consists of the date recorded, patient ID, doctor ID, diagnosis, treatment plan, prescriptions and medical services provided to the patient. The medical record entry is uniquely identified by the entry ID.
Since:
2024-10-27
